<h2>License</h2>
<p>Open Discovery is user-supported open-source software though previous  versions are freely available,The operating system is built with open source and free software and restricted for academic and personal purposes only there is no commercial license.</p>
<h2>Minimum System requirements</h2>
<p>Intel/AMD 2.0 Ghz Dual core cpu or Higher, Min of 2 GB RAM,  256 Mb integrated or dedicated Graphics, DVD optical drive and 20 GB Hard Disk space</p>
 
